Welcome

Thanks for participing in this chain-transmission experiment.

To begin, click on Continue.

Welcome to this transmission chain experiment! This study explores the difficulty of spelling specific names.

You will be asked to spell the last name of a celebrity appearing on the screen. You will be shown a picture of the celebrity and an audio of his*her name.

Good luck!
